PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FFamily and friends of David 'Syd'
OL,8,FLawrence, the first British-born black
OL,9,Fcricketer to represent England, have
OL,10,Fremembered a 'trailblazer' in a new
OL,11,Ffilm reflecting his remarkable life
OL,12,Fand legacy.
OL,14,FDavid Valentine Lawrence,
OL,15,Faffectionately known as Syd, died at
OL,16,Fthe age of 61, a year after revealing
OL,17,Fpublicly he had been diagnosed with
OL,18,FMotor Neurone Disease.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
