FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FThe diagnosis devastated Syd and his
OL,8,Ffamily, confronting them with a
OL,9,Fdisease that would gradually steal
OL,10,Ffrom a loving father, brother, and
OL,11,Fhusband his ability to walk`and
OL,12,Feventually, talk.
OL,14,FBut in the memories of those who knew
OL,15,Fhim best, Syd was a man with a
OL,16,Fboundless energy, passion, and true
OL,17,Fdetermination to succeed in whatever
OL,18,Fhe did, on or off the pitch.
OL,20,FWatch 'Syd' on ITVX now
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
