FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FIn the film, 'Syd', stars of the
OL,8,Fcricketing world, including friends
OL,9,Fand former teammates Phil Tufnell and
OL,10,FJack Russell, former player and
OL,11,Fcommentator Jonathan Agnew and West
OL,12,FIndies cricket legend Sir Viv
OL,13,FRichards, recount their memories of
OL,14,Fthe man who never gave up.
OL,16,FFast-bowler Syd was the first British-
OL,17,Fborn black cricketer to represent
OL,18,FEngland, and was known for his
OL,19,Faggressive style.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"As soon as he started playing cricket
OL,8,Fhe was going to play for England",
OL,9,FSyd's wife Gaynor Lawrence told ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,F"He had that mentality. Whatever he
OL,13,Fdid, he just succeeded", she said.
OL,15,F'Hissing Syd': A fast bowler with
OL,16,F'fearsome' pace
OL,18,F"Hissing Syd," we used to call him",
OL,19,Fsaid former England player Phil
OL,20,FTufnell, remembering his close friend
OL,21,Fand former teammate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"He'd try and knock your head off. He
OL,8,Fjust had that bustling run up and then
OL,9,Farms and legs and then, whoosh."
OL,11,FCommentator and former England player
OL,12,FJonathan Agnew described Syd as a
OL,13,F"rolling ball of energy and effort"
OL,14,Fwho was like "gold dust" to watch.
OL,16,F"As he ran into bowl - puffing,
OL,17,Fwheezing, whistling, everything
OL,18,Fresulting in this massive leap and
OL,19,Fclimax at the crease as he literally
OL,20,Fhurled himself into every ball", the
OL,21,Fbroadcaster said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"From a commentator's perspective Syd
OL,8,Fwas gold dust because you just had
OL,9,Fsomething going on all the time. There
OL,10,Fwas just this vision of this enormous
OL,11,Fman, shirt busting open, sweating,
OL,12,Ftrying 150% every ball, and there he
OL,13,Fis tearing in, trying to get
OL,14,Fsomething, often out of nothing."
OL,16,FSyd's career began in Gloucestershire,
OL,17,Fwhere in 1981 he secured a place in
OL,18,Fthe county's first team, bringing a
OL,19,F"breath of fresh air" to the squad,
OL,20,Faccording to fellow teammate Andy
OL,21,FBrassington.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
