FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"He came in all guns blazing", he said.
OL,9,F"He lived his life on the front foot,
OL,10,Fand it was no different here. It must
OL,11,Fhave been a massive move for him to
OL,12,Fcome from Gloucester and playing club
OL,13,Fcricket into a professional setup.
OL,15,F"He was a wild young man who upset the
OL,16,Fapple cart now and again and
OL,17,Fespecially in his first few weeks here.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"It's no secret that he got arrested a
OL,8,Fcouple of times, and it was Tony Brown
OL,9,Fthe club captain and a legend of
OL,10,FGloucestershire who got him out of the
OL,11,Fpolice cell and a few days later, took
OL,12,Fhim down to see Viv Richards, and Viv
OL,13,Fsat him in a room for an hour and told
OL,14,FSyd what to do and not what to do. It
OL,15,Fcompletely changed Syd's life."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FRemembering that very interaction, Sir
OL,8,FViv Richards told ITV News: "I think
OL,9,Fhe was pretty much a rookie then, and
OL,10,FI think they had some issues with him,
OL,11,Fmaybe wanting to, knowing of his
OL,12,Fpotential. They just wanted someone to
OL,13,Fbe in his ears.
OL,15,F"And I remember I did that, and I can
OL,16,Fremember after a few years, he would
OL,17,Fcome and say 'thank you', which I
OL,18,Freally appreciated."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
