FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F'I'd never heard my big mate scream
OL,8,Flike that before': The devastating
OL,9,Finjury that changed everything
OL,11,FBy 1992, Syd Lawrence was a firm
OL,12,Ffavourite in the England cricket
OL,13,Fsetup. As a fast bowler, he had
OL,14,Festablished himself within the team.
OL,16,FBut during the last day of a Test
OL,17,Fmatch at Wellington in New Zealand, he
OL,18,Fsuffered a terrible knee injury,
OL,19,Fdescribed as one of the worst in
OL,20,Fsporting history.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FJack Russell, former England teammate
OL,8,Fand friend, says he vividly remembers
OL,9,Fthe day.
OL,11,F"You can still hear the noise of his
OL,12,Fkneecap cracking", he said. "If you
OL,13,Fbang two cricket bats together very
OL,14,Floudly next to your ear, that was the
OL,15,Fsound, which I can still hear.
OL,17,F"He was screaming... I was upset
OL,18,Fbecause I'd never heard my big mate
OL,19,Fscream like that before", he added.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FSyd's sister, Dianne Lawrence,
OL,8,Fdescribed the injury as "devastating"
OL,9,Ffor her brother and the whole family.
OL,11,F"It wasn't great because we
OL,12,Fautomatically thought his career had
OL,13,Fended there and then, and Dave wasn't
OL,14,Fa crier, and to see him cry in pain,
OL,15,Fthat must have hurt."
OL,17,FSyd and wife Gaynor had only just had
OL,18,Ftheir son, Buster, at the time of the
OL,19,Finjury.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"He was so determined he was going to
OL,8,Fget back playing again", Gaynor said.
OL,9,F"His focus was completely on his rehab
OL,10,Fand training and everything. So it was
OL,11,Fhard. It was very hard for all of us."
OL,13,F"What a lot of people forget is when
OL,14,Fhe actually got injured, he was right
OL,15,Fat the top of his game", said Andy
OL,16,FBrassington.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"He was playing for England,
OL,8,Fperforming well, and he's right at the
OL,9,Ftop, and suddenly he's taken away from
OL,10,Fit. He could have gone completely to
OL,11,Fpot, in all honesty. But what he did,
OL,12,Fhe rolled his sleeves up and got on
OL,13,Fwith it and he wanted to prove a point
OL,14,Fthat he could come back from it".
OL,16,FJack Russell said: "Nobody had seen an
OL,17,Finjury like that before, so we didn't
OL,18,Fknow how long that was going to take,
OL,19,Fbut you know we'd hoped, fingers
OL,20,Fcrossed, that he would come back and
OL,21,Fstill bowl quick".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FBut with time, the prospect of getting
OL,8,Fback to the professional game became
OL,9,Fharder to reach, so Syd began his
OL,10,Fsearch for new challenges.
OL,12,FSyd Lawrence: The presenter, nightclub
OL,13,Fowner, bodybuilder and cricket club
OL,14,Fpresident
OL,16,FSyd went on to become a nightclub
OL,17,Fowner, a competitive bodybuilder, a
OL,18,Ftelevision presenter and a leading
OL,19,Fadvocate for inclusion and diversity
OL,20,Fin his role as president of
OL,21,FGloucestershire County Cricket Club.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FHis spell as a presenter on Time Out
OL,8,FWest showed Syd's humour and 'love for
OL,9,Flife', his family said.
OL,11,F"I've seen lots of clips, but I don't
OL,12,Fremember any of it, really, live",
OL,13,FSyd's son Buster said.
OL,15,F"I've seen enough of it (since) and I
OL,16,Fknow he's quite a character. He seemed
OL,17,Fto come alive when he got in front of
OL,18,Fa camera. He wasn't shy, that is for
OL,19,Fsure.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"He always had a love for life and a
OL,8,Flove for people."
OL,10,FIt was at the age of 50 that Syd
OL,11,Fdecided to become a professional
OL,12,Fbodybuilder and went on to compete on
OL,13,Fthe national stage.
OL,15,FOwner of Bristol's Trojan Gym, Matt
OL,16,FHudd, trained with Syd through that
OL,17,Fperiod, when he competed to the
OL,18,Fhighest level, even going on to win
OL,19,Fthe Mr Britain competition.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"You look at him, you think, 'Wow,
OL,8,Fhe's massive', but never judge a book
OL,9,Fby its cover", Matt said.
OL,11,F"When he's training, he's loud making
OL,12,Fall these crazy noises. And the next
OL,13,Fthing I know, he's helping out a 19-
OL,14,Fyear-old lad who's just started
OL,15,Fbodybuilding - and then they're
OL,16,Ftraining together. These guys didn't
OL,17,Fknow he was a famous cricket player."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"It was just incredible what he put
OL,8,Fhis mind to", said Gaynor. "He would
OL,9,Fjust do it. He was very strong-minded
OL,10,Fand strong-willed.
OL,12,F"The first time we saw him on stage
OL,13,F(competing as a bodybuilder) I
OL,14,Fcouldn't actually believe that that
OL,15,Fwas him up there."
OL,17,FGloucestershire County Cricket club
OL,18,Fpresident
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
