FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43720
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FIn 2020, cricket came under the
OL,8,Fspotlight as Yorkshire player Azeem
OL,9,FRafiq spoke out against the racism he
OL,10,Ffaced at the club, telling MPs the
OL,11,Fgame was institutionally racist.
OL,13,FSince those revelations, the English
OL,14,FCricket Board say significant progress
OL,15,Fhas been made to make the game more
OL,16,Finclusive and to tackle discrimination.
OL,18,FFor Syd, Azeem Rafiq's comments
OL,19,Fstirred painful memories from his own
OL,20,Fplaying days.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G20/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43721
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"He was very aware that not everybody
OL,8,Fout there liked big black fast
OL,9,Fbowlers, and he was well aware of the
OL,10,Fsituation with his colour", Andy
OL,11,FBrassington said.
OL,13,F"It's well known and it's documented
OL,14,Fthat there was an incident where
OL,15,Fsomeone put a banana outside Syd's
OL,16,Froom.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G21/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43722
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"Syd's reaction to that was
OL,8,Faggression. He certainly didn't want
OL,9,Fanyone to know that he was hurt, but I
OL,10,Ftalked to him a lot and it hurt him
OL,11,Fdeeply."
OL,13,FIn 2022, Syd became the new President
OL,14,Fof Gloucestershire Cricket, making him
OL,15,Fthe first black man to be become
OL,16,Fpresident of a professional English
OL,17,Fcricket club.
OL,19,F"He always championed the underdog",
OL,20,FPhil Tufnell said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G22/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43723
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"And I think that's another reason why
OL,8,FI got on very well with him, because I
OL,9,Fwas always a little bit of an
OL,10,Funderdog, always getting in a bit of
OL,11,Ftrouble or saying the wrong thing at
OL,12,Fthe wrong time.
OL,14,F"He'd never judge you, and I think
OL,15,Fthat when he got that opportunity with
OL,16,FGloucester (as president), he thought
OL,17,Fhe could really do good".
OL,19,F"The presidency was a godsend for
OL,20,Fhim", Andy Brassington said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G23/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43724
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"I had a phone call from him at 7am
OL,8,Fone morning and he said: 'Brass,
OL,9,Fnobody knows, but the club has just
OL,10,Fasked me to be the president. What do
OL,11,Fyou think? I don't think I'm going to
OL,12,Faccept it because everyone will say
OL,13,FI'm the president because I'm a black
OL,14,Fman.'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G24/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43725
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"I said: 'Whoa, hold on. Let's just
OL,8,Fbreak this down a minute: Local boy
OL,9,Ffrom Gloucester. Played for your
OL,10,Fcounty, played for your country,
OL,11,Fsuccessful business person, a role
OL,12,Fmodel for so many people out there. It
OL,13,Fdidn't matter if you're pink or green,
OL,14,Fmate. That's not it at all. This is
OL,15,FSyd Lawrence becoming our president'."
OL,17,F"He did a fantastic job. He brought so
OL,18,Fmany new things to the table. He
OL,19,Fopened up a lot of areas that people
OL,20,Fwere afraid to talk about."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G25/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43726
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F2024: MND diagnosis
OL,9,FIn the summer of 2024, Syd's world was
OL,10,Fturned upside down when he was
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with motor neurone disease.
OL,13,FHe'd undergone a knee replacement
OL,14,Foperation following his injury, and
OL,15,Fthe recovery was a painful process,
OL,16,Fhis family say.
OL,18,F"He kept falling over", Gaynor said.
OL,19,F"He fell down the steps outside, fell
OL,20,Fdown the house steps. It was really,
OL,21,Freally bad".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G26/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43727
SC,0027
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FHe was taken to hospital where doctors
OL,8,Fcarried out tests. Eventually, they
OL,9,Ffound traces of MND in his tongue,
OL,10,Fwhich meant Syd lost his voice very
OL,11,Fquickly.
OL,13,F"For a chap like Syd I don't think
OL,14,Fthere could have been a worse disease,
OL,15,Fbecause it just sort of ate him away",
OL,16,FPhil Tufnell said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G27/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43728
SC,0028
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"He struggled like anyone would don't
OL,8,Fget me wrong", Buster said. "The first
OL,9,Ffew months were tough. We had a good
OL,10,Fgroup of friends, and family, and
OL,11,Fwonderful carers too."
OL,13,FOver the next few months, Syd was
OL,14,Fdetermined to raise awareness of MND,
OL,15,Fhosting events to fundraise for
OL,16,Fresearch around the disease. But soon,
OL,17,Fhis condition rapidly deteriorated.
OL,19,F"He'd sort of stopped eating", Gaynor
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G28/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43729
SC,0029
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"He couldn't swallow for the last
OL,8,Fcouple of weeks. And then the fluids
OL,9,Fdidn't go down either. And so we knew
OL,10,Fit was going to be pretty soon after
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,F"He didn't have anything left in him.
OL,14,FHe was just hanging on, really, to see
OL,15,Ffamily and friends", Buster said.
OL,17,F"It wasn't nice for him. And by the
OL,18,Fend, he even said he was ready."
OL,26,@sD@FO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G29/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43730
SC,0030
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FAndy Brassington remembered the last
OL,8,Ftime he saw Syd. "When I left Syd on
OL,9,Fthat Saturday morning and I went
OL,10,Foutside (it was) so funny, the sun
OL,11,Fcame out, everything went still,
OL,12,Feverything stopped.
OL,14,F"And I looked up at the sky and I just
OL,15,Fthought to myself 'This is the time
OL,16,Ffor him to go.' And when I had the
OL,17,Fphone call, I just thought of that,
OL,18,Fthat stillness as if everything had
OL,19,Fstopped.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G30/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43731
SC,0031
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"And I thought, yeah, he knew he was
OL,8,Fgoing. He hung on to say goodbyes."
OL,10,FPhil Tufnell remembers Syd as a
OL,11,Ftrusted and dear friend.
OL,13,F"He was probably one of my best
OL,14,Ffriends if not, you know, one of my
OL,15,Fmost trusted friends, not just in
OL,16,Fcricket, but in life.
OL,18,F"He was someone that you could always
OL,19,Fphone up and rely on to help you out
OL,20,Fif you needed it".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G31/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43732
SC,0032
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,FJack Russell said: "He was just one of
OL,8,Fthose special people that come along
OL,9,Fevery so often. He was definitely a
OL,10,Ftrailblazer.
OL,12,F"But the big thing that sticks in my
OL,13,Fhead is a perfect example of giving it
OL,14,Fyour best shot and never giving up and
OL,15,Fgiving it 100%. And in the world we
OL,16,Flive in, that's probably quite a good
OL,17,Fasset to have", he added.
OL,19,F"He was just lovely", said Gaynor.
OL,20,F"Everything he did, he put over 100%
OL,21,Fin and just had fun.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G32/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43733
SC,0033
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772193826
OL,3,CThe remarkable life story of'
OL,4,Ctrailblazing' cricket legend David
OL,5,C'Syd' Lawrence
OL,7,F"We always said we've had a great life
OL,8,Fand we kept saying that when he was
OL,9,Fill. We've done so much together. Good
OL,10,Fmemories", said Gaynor.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G33/33
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
